fields.name: ApplicationSharingPolicy
fields.description: Policy for sharing applications on this compute instance among users of parent workspace. If Personal, only the creator can access applications on this compute instance. When Shared, any workspace user can access applications on this instance depending on his/her assigned role.

fields.name: Applications
fields.description: Describes available applications and their endpoints on this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: ComputeInstanceAuthorizationType
fields.description: The Compute Instance Authorization type. Available values are personal (default).

fields.name: ConnectivityEndpoints
fields.description: Describes all connectivity endpoints available for this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: Containers
fields.description: Describes informations of containers on this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: Describes information on user who created this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: CustomServices
fields.description: List of Custom Services added to the compute.

fields.name: DataDisks
fields.description: Describes informations of dataDisks on this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: DataMounts
fields.description: Describes informations of dataMounts on this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: EnableNodePublicIP
fields.description: Enable or disable node public IP address provisioning. Possible values are: Possible values are: true - Indicates that the compute nodes will have public IPs provisioned. false - Indicates that the compute nodes will have a private endpoint and no public IPs.

fields.name: Errors
fields.description: Collection of errors encountered on this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: LastOperation
fields.description: The last operation on ComputeInstance.

fields.name: OsImageMetadata
fields.description: Returns metadata about the operating system image for this compute instance.

fields.name: PersonalComputeInstanceSettings
fields.description: Settings for a personal compute instance.

fields.name: Schedules
fields.description: The list of schedules to be applied on the computes.

fields.name: SetupScripts
fields.description: Details of customized scripts to execute for setting up the cluster.

fields.name: SshSettings
fields.description: Specifies policy and settings for SSH access.

fields.name: State
fields.description: The current state of this ComputeInstance.

fields.name: Subnet
fields.description: Virtual network subnet resource ID the compute nodes belong to.

fields.name: VMSize
fields.description: Virtual Machine Size

fields.name: Versions
fields.description: ComputeInstance version.
